			<div class="entry clearfix post">
				<h1 class="title">Welcome to Belfield Public School</h1>
				
								
				<h2><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">CORONAVIRUS (COVID-19) INFORMATION</span></strong></h2>
<h4><span style="color: #008000;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">MEAL DISTRIBUTION INFO</span></em></span></h4>
<p><span style="color: #008000;">Please use the following route when picking up school meals.  Meals will be distributed by door #7 (East side gym door).  Distribution time will be from 11:00 AM to 12:30 PM.  DO NOT COME INTO THE SCHOOL TO GET MEALS.</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: #008000;">Cars enter driveway on east side of school – 4th St NE</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #008000;">Stop at pick up location – Meals will be brought to your vehicle</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #008000;">Exit to the north onto 4th Ave NE</span></li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://www.health.nd.gov/diseases-conditions/coronavirus" target="_blank">North Dakota Department of Health (NDDOH) website</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/schools-childcare/guidance-for-schools.html" target="_blank">Centers for Disease Control and Prevention website</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/schools-childcare/schools-faq.html" target="_blank">Specific FAQs for K-12 Schools from CDC</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.nd.gov/dpi/nddpi-updates-and-guidance-covid-19" target="_blank">North Dakota Department of Public Instruction – Covid-19 Updates &amp; Guidance</a></p>
<p>ALL BELFIELD PUBLIC SCHOOLS ACTIVITIES (ATHLETIC &amp; NON-ATHLETIC) ARE SUSPENDED UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE.  WE WILL EVALUATE THE SITUATION ON A WEEKLY BASIS.</p>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Breakfast &amp; Lunch Program</span></h2>
<p>Pickups will be on Tuesday April 14, from 11-12:30.</p>
<p>From here on out, all orders must be placed by Tuesday of the week prior and pickups will be on the following Monday.</p>
<p> </p>
<ul>
<li><a style="color: blue;" href="http://www.belfield.k12.nd.us/online-educational-resources/" target="_blank">CLICK HERE for a list of FREE online educational resources</a></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><iframe style="border: 0;" src="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=cgsuungfmvg51lfot8t40uj8us%40group.calendar.google.com&amp;ctz=America%2FDenver" width="600" height="600" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></p>
<h2></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<strong><em><span style="color: #000080;">NOW AVAILABLE –</span></em></strong><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;"> <a style="color: #000080; text-decoration: underline;" href="http://www.belfield.k12.nd.us/files/2020/02/2020-2021.pdf" target="_blank">2020-2021 SCHOOL CALENDAR</a></span></span></em>
</li>
</ul>
